snippet.title: CIBOS Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
CIBOS is a crazy party game, up to 4-players online or local centering around hilarious versus matches. Dash your opponent, collect power-up and bolts to become the best employee of the galaxy!!! Also experience a solo adventure to discover the amazing world of CIBOS!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/728090/CIBOS/
